datasets.name: dataset_20
queryLines: SELECT Geo_Country_Code AS Country, MEASURE(Active_Devices) AS MAU, MEASURE(Active_Devices) / SUM(MEASURE(Active_Devices)) OVER (PARTITION BY Geo_Country_Code) AS Percent_Active_Devices_By_Country, RANK() OVER (ORDER BY MEASURE(Active_Devices) DESC) AS f_active_devices_rank FROM hpx_events_model WHERE Event_Date_Time >= '2023-05-01' AND App_Version IS NOT NULL AND App_Version != 'not a store release' GROUP BY Geo_Country_Code ORDER BY Percent_Active_Devices_By_Country DESC
